{"tid":942820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波倡放寬一帶一路國家簽證刺激香港旅遊","createTime":"2018-12-16T05:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T02:45:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ead0ffffab0d88405af166d00b9089198c5c31a2","tid":942820,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"陳茂波倡放寬一帶一路國家簽證刺激香港旅遊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E5%80%A1%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC-%E5%B8%B6-%E8%B7%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A-034923107.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC-%25E5%25B8%25B6-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2588%25BA%25E6%25BF%2580%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A-034923107.html&d=CKAMKtmgZZ4JHF8XMmphFm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5d0f163f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E5%80%A1%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC-%E5%B8%B6-%E8%B7%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A-034923107.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】財政司司長陳茂波在網誌指，考慮向一帶一路的國家和地區放寬簽證安排。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波指，今年十月單月訪港旅客已逾580萬人次。隨着港珠澳大橋開通，預計今年全年的旅客量將超過六千萬人次，打破2014年歷來最高紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波指，一程多站是現時訪港旅客的大趨勢，香港要不斷優化旅遊資源及加強對外推廣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現時全球約170個國家和地區的人民可免簽證到港旅遊或參與商務。陳茂波展望未來政府會繼續考慮向其他不同地方，包括一帶一路的國家和地區，放寬相關簽證安排，促進國際文化和旅遊交流。<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"9824d0ec8326e5c27c28067fe5c30564559625ec","tid":942820,"uid":196924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T06:15:05.000Z","msg":"港共比中共更重視一帶一路"},{"pid":"b97c13fbd30a8ecf35a4cf74ab4c8f3098c46885","tid":942820,"uid":89530,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"仲唔撚夠刺